  "description": "<p><strong>Position Summary</strong><br />\nAs a GP  you will play a vital role in diagnosing, treating, and managing medical conditions commonly encountered in general practice. <br />\n<strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>\n• To provide medical Expertise:<br />\n• To diagnose, treat, and manage a broad spectrum of medical conditions.<br />\n• To promote preventive healthcare practices to improve patient outcomes.<br />\n• To support the efficient operation of the clinic, including managing patient\nrecords, coordinating care services, and overseeing patient scheduling.</p><p><strong>\nQualifications</strong><br />\n• Medical Registration:<br />\n• Must be fully registered with the Singapore Medical Council (SMC).\n</p><p>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</p><p><u><strong></strong></u><a href=\"mailto:valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u><strong>valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></a><u><strong></strong></u></p><p>EA Personnel: Valerie Yong Kian Fung</p><p>CEI No.: R1103704</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
